\c 1
\s Kufara kwavanoda Mwari,
\s nokusafara kwavasingadi Mwari
\p
\v 1 Akakomborerwa munhu asingafambi panorangana vakaipa, Asingamiri panzira yavatadzi, Asingagari panogara vadadi.
\v 2 Asi anofarira murayiro waJehovha; Anofungisisa murayiro wake masikati nousiku.
\p
\v 3 Achafanana nomuti wakasimwa pahova dzemvura,
\s Anobereka michero yawo nenguva yawo,
\s Mashizha awo haasvavi;
\s Chinhu chipi nechipi chaanoita chichaendika.
\p
\v 4 Vakaipa havana kudaro;
\s Asi vakafanana nehundi inopepereswa nemhepo.
\p
\v 5 Naizvozvo vakaipa havangamiri pakutongeswa,
\p Navatadzi paungano yavakarurama.
\v 6 Nokuti Jehovha anoziva nzira yavakarurama;
\s Asi nzira yavakaipa ichaparadzwa.
